"or `shutdown` method are automatically enlisted with a destruction "
"callback. If you have a public `close` or `shutdown` method and you do not "
"wish for it to be called when the container shuts down, you can add "
"`@Bean(destroyMethod = \"\")` to your bean definition to disable the default "
"`(inferred)` mode."
